            <p>Inhaste</p>
            <p>
                <persName role="author">Isaac Hart</persName>
            </p>
            <p>I was at rehearsal on<lb/>
                <date>Sunday</date> last. <persName>Lehache<add>?</add></persName> is<lb/> the
                Leader. The music is beautiful &amp; well sang<lb/> The synagogue inside is very
                much like<lb/> the one on <placeName>Rampart St</placeName><lb/> The old pulpit is
                between the allmoner<lb/> &amp; Nichol</p>
